PrecisAppointment of Emer G. Robles, of North Vancouver, British Columbia, as a full-time permanent member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Vancouver Regional Office) to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and designation of the said Emer G. Robles as an Assistant Deputy Chairman of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Vancouver Regional Office), effective November 1, 1991.
